# --- Legacy flat-file storage (pre-Postgres) ---------------------------------
# The app used to persist everything in these gitignored JSON files, one per
# concern. As of the Postgres/Prisma migration, all persistence lives in
# Postgres instead (see prisma/schema.prisma, DATABASE_URL in .env.local, and
# `npm run db:migrate`). These entries are kept around only in case a local
# checkout still has one of these stale files sitting in the project root —
# they should never be committed either way.
.ai-settings.local.json
.auth-users.local.json
.projects-data.local.json
.budget-templates.local.json
